OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer and Chancellor Rachel
OL,7,FReeves have decided to means-test the
OL,8,Fbenefits, worth up to #300, which they
OL,9,Finsist is necessary to help fill a
OL,10,F"#22 billion black hole" in the public
OL,11,Ffinances.
OL,13,FFrom this winter, only people on
OL,14,Fpension credit or certain other
OL,15,Fbenefits will receive the payments,
OL,16,Fwhile about 10 million others are set
OL,17,Fto be stripped of the allowance.
